description:
Are you passionate about off-grid country living, exploring the 
intricacies of agriculture, and acquiring comprehensive insights on how 
to become self-sustaining? Are you young and interested in volunteering 
at Amazing Discoveries? We invite you to join us on the farm! Reach out 
to us via email to discover how you can join and learn alongside us.

If you are eager to learn how to live off the grid, discover these techniques and more with us!

Contact us: 1-866-572-9457 or email us at client-care@amazingdiscoveries.org with the subject line-  I Want To Help At The Farm!

We look forward to hearing from you soon!
Thank you for watching our short video. If you have questions or would like to support Amazing
